## ÁREA 2: Estado del Proyecto vs. Expectativas 📈

### Diagnóstico de Madurez

```
Prototipo ─── MVP ─── Beta ──── Production-Ready
                               ▲
                               └── AQUÍ (85-90%)
```

**Veredicto: Late Beta / Pre-Production.** El core funcional está completo y testeado (1488 tests). Sin embargo, faltan items de producción real:

### Lo que ESTÁ hecho (completado)

| Área | Items | Estado |
|:-----|:------|:-------|
| Auth + RBAC | JWT, 8 roles, login hardening, MFA | ✅ |
| API Gateway | 8 Edge Functions, write ops server-side | ✅ |
| Offline-First | IndexedDB (Dexie v7), sync queue, DLQ, Web Locks | ✅ |
| NZ Compliance | Breaks, wages, work hours, server-side enforcement | ✅ |
| Payroll | Server-side calculation, timesheet approval, export PDF/CSV | ✅ |
| Fraud Detection | 3-rule smart engine (server + fallback) | ✅ |
| HHRR | Empleados, contratos, visa tracking, compliance alerts | ✅ |
| Logistics | Fleet tracking, bin inventory, transport requests | ✅ |
| Messaging | Chat rooms, direct/group, realtime subscriptions | ✅ |
| QC/Quality Control | Inspections, grades, history tracking | ✅ |
| Orchard Map | Block/row assignment, visual heatmap | ✅ |
| Security | RLS, rate limiting (60/min), CORS, input validation (Zod) | ✅ |
| Gateway Resilience | Retry 502/504 with backoff, timeout, UI degradation | ✅ |
| Dark Mode | CSS overrides, useTheme, localStorage persistence | ✅ |
| Date/Dropdown UI | DatePicker, Dropdown (searchable, keyboard nav) | ✅ |

