## ÁREA 3: Auditoría Arquitectónica (Visión Macro) 🏗️

### Stack Tecnológico

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Client (PWA)"
        UI[React + Vite + Capacitor]
        IDB[(IndexedDB / Dexie v7)]
        SW[Service Worker]
    end

    subgraph "API Gateway"
        EF1[approve-timesheet]
        EF2[calculate-payroll]
        EF3[check-compliance]
        EF4[detect-anomalies]
        EF5[manage-admin]
        EF6[manage-attendance]
        EF7[record-bucket]
        EF8[submit-audit-log]
    end

    subgraph "Backend (Supabase)"
        PG[(PostgreSQL + RLS)]
        AUTH[Supabase Auth]
        RT[Realtime]
    end

    UI --> EF1 & EF2 & EF3 & EF4 & EF5 & EF6 & EF7 & EF8
    UI --> IDB
    IDB --> UI
    EF1 & EF2 & EF3 & EF4 & EF5 & EF6 & EF7 & EF8 --> PG
    UI --> AUTH
    UI --> RT
```

**Veredicto arquitectónico:** ✅ **Sólida.** La separación en 3 capas (UI → Edge Functions → PostgreSQL) es production-grade. El patrón Repository aísla Supabase completamente (verificado: 22 repositorios, 0 imports directos de `supabase` en servicios excepto [authContext.repository.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/src/repositories/authContext.repository.ts) con retry ya integrado).

### Sistema Offline-First

**Evaluación detallada basada en código:**

| Componente | Archivo | Estado |
|:-----------|:--------|:-------|
| Sync Queue (IndexedDB) | [db.ts L54-61](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/db.ts) | ✅ 10 tipos soportados |
| Cross-tab Mutex | [sync.service.ts L61-68](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/sync.service.ts) | ✅ Web Locks API |
| Dead Letter Queue | [db.ts L42-51](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/db.ts) | ✅ Persistente en IDB |
| Error categorization | [sync.service.ts L260-284](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/sync.service.ts) | ✅ network/server/validation/unknown |
| Network abort on offline | [sync.service.ts L146-149](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/sync.service.ts) | ✅ Early exit |
| Conflict detection | [conflict.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/conflict.service.ts) | ✅ 9.2KB, full resolution UI |
| Optimistic Locking | [optimistic-lock.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/optimistic-lock.service.ts) | ✅ `updated_at` check |
| Auto-reconnect sync | [sync.service.ts L292-294](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/sync.service.ts) | ✅ Immediate on `online` event |

**Veredicto offline:** ✅ **Enterprise-grade.** DLQ, mutex, error classification, optimistic locking, conflict resolution — esto supera a la mayoría de apps de campo del mercado.

### Seguridad Estructural

| Capa | Mecanismo | Archivo | Estado |
|:-----|:----------|:--------|:-------|
