| Login Hardening | Intentos, lockout, device fingerprint | [authHardening.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/services/authHardening.service.ts) | ✅ |
| MFA | TOTP two-factor | [useMFA.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20(1)/src/hooks/useMFA.ts) | ✅ |
